name: Dina Borjal
body: This is to report a recurring issue observed in the complaint submission system. Over the past week, several users have reported that their entries are not being saved correctly, resulting in missing data in the database. I tested the workflow myself and confirmed that the error occurs when multiple fields are submitted simultaneously. I recommend that the technical team investigate the input validation and database handling to ensure data integrity and prevent further disruptions.

Despite multiple attempts to submit my request, the system repeatedly displayed errors and prevented me from completing the process. name: Yesha Magsombol
body: I wanted to share some feedback about the new dashboard interface. The updated design feels modern and user-friendly, and the navigation is much clearer compared to the previous version. However, I noticed that certain buttons are not responsive on mobile devices, which makes it difficult to access features on the go. Overall, the improvements are appreciated, and I hope the mobile experience can be optimized further.
